    "title": "Marico Advisory Limited is Hiring: Quality Control Engineer (Entry-Level)",
    "description": "Marico Advisory Limited is actively seeking a talented and motivated Quality Control Engineer to join our dynamic team in Bengaluru. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Marico Advisory Limited:\nMarico Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement lean manufacturing and continuous improvement initiatives\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Six Sigma\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n• Proficiency in FMEA\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in Statistical Process Control\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Flexible working hours\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bengaluru, Karnataka, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Marico Advisory Limited!",
